AD | ☀️Summer skin but make it effortless.
I’ve been trying out the new Bronzing Balm by @subtlbeauty and let me just say, this one melts right into the skin.

It just launched in five shades:
✨ Biscotti – light with neutral undertones
✨ Caramel – tan with golden tones
✨ Toffee – tan bronze with warm tones (the one I’m wearing!)
✨ Truffle – deep bronze with warm undertones
✨ Ganache – rich with cool undertones

I’m using Toffee in this look and it gives me the perfect sun-kissed warmth without looking or feeling heavy. The texture is buttery, super blendable, and it literally takes me less than a minute to apply.

I topped it off with a bit of highlighter and called it a day!! Clean, glowy, summer-ready skin. 🌞

➡️ If you love easy, on-the-go makeup, definitely check this one out, especially if you’re already a fan of the Subtl stack!

Let me know if you try it or want help picking a shade!

latestPosts.caption:
It all started with a simple U.S. map puzzle and a very curious 3.5-year-old asking, ‘What state is this?’ 🗺️ 

Her curiosity took the lead, and before we knew it, she was reciting all 50 states! 😍 Not something we ever pushed for, just something she genuinely enjoyed and wanted to learn on her own.
And yes, some pronunciations are totally toddler-style, so feel free to listen with love, not grammar ears. 💕 

So proud of her little mind and the way it explores the world. 💛
